Privacy Policy

We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect email addresses and basic contact information for communication purposes only.

2. How We Use Information
Email addresses are used solely to send informational or service-related messages.
We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties.

3. Email Communication
Recipients may receive emails because they have interacted with our services or public business listings.
All recipients can reply to request removal from future communications.

4. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect personal data.

5. Contact
If you have any questions or requests regarding your data, please contact us at:
support@helpsender.net
